 {This course is structured with 25 chapters which can be grouped together in the following way:   - Introduction chapter (you are here)   - What is 'Compensation?' chapter   - Three Quickstarter chapters: Benko Gambit Half/Fully Accepted, Benko Gambit Declined, and Non-Benko Gambit Lines.  - Two Benko Gambit Fully Accepted chapters: #1 and #2.  - Four Benko Gambit Half-Accepted chapters: #1, #2, 3, and #4.  - Three Benko Gambit Declined chapters: #1, #2, and a3.  - Nine Non-Benko Gambit chapters.   - Model Games chapter.   - My Blitz Games chapter.   - Puzzles chapter.} 1. --
