19. Qf1+
20. Kd2
20. Bh6+
21. Kc3
21. Qxa1
22. Qxa8
22. Qc1+ {Time to hunt the king down. Other moves work too but this is the quickest route.} 
23. Kxb3
23. Qd1+
24. Ka3
24. Qd3+
25. b3
25. Bc1+
26. Ka4
26. Nb6+
27. Ka5
27. Bd2+
28. b4
28. Bxb4 {A nice finish :-)} 
