38. Kh8 {The correct square.A)38...Kg6?39.Qxe4+Kh5(39...Qf5??40.Qe8+Rf741.Qg8+Kh542.Qxf7++-)(39...Rf5??40.Qe8+Kf641.Qf7+Ke542.Re7+Kf443.Qc4+Kg344.Qg4)40.Qg4+Kg641.Qe4+=The game ends in a draw. If Black tries too hard to win here they will end up blundering.B)38...Kg8??39.Qc8+Rf840.Qe6+Rf741.Qg6+Kf842.Qxh6+Ke843.Qh8+Rf844.Ra8+Ke745.Qg7+Rf746.Ra7+Ke647.Qg6+Now the queen will circle around black's king.47...Qf648.Qxe4+Qe549.Qc4+d550.Qa6+Qd651.Qxd6+Kxd652.Rxf7+-C)38...Rf7!Blocking with the rook would work here too.39.Qxe4+Kg7-+} 
