[Result "*"]

15. f4 {White's knight doesn't have a good square to move to and avoid losing material.} 
16. Nc2 {16.Ng4h5The knight is running low on squares.17.Nh6+Trying to take advantage of our bishop needing to defend the d4-knight.17...Kh7The king threatens to capture the knight on h6.18.Nxf7Qf6-+The knight is trapped and we will win two pieces for a rook next move with ...Rxf7.} 
16. Nxc2
17. Qxc2
17. Qxd5 {We win a piece due to the pin along the c-file.} 
