*
[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
[Round "?"]
[White "Puzzles"]
[Black "Levin, Felix vs. Ellers, Holger"]
[FEN "1rb1k2r/4bppp/pPp5/2p5/4Q3/4P3/q2B1PPP/1R2KB1R b Kk - 0 15"]
[Result "*"]

15. f5 {White's queen is going to have a hard time defending the rook on b1.} 
16. Bc4 {Trying to counterattack black's queen.16.Qxc6+Bd7-+White cannot save both the queen and b1-rook.16.Qd3Trying to keep the rook defended.16...c4!The queen cannot maintain contact with the rook on b1 anymore.} 
16. Qxd2+ {A winning desperado. Black eliminates the bishop on d2 before capturing white's queen.} 
17. Kxd2
17. fxe4 {Black is ahead a piece and winning.} 
*
[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
[Round "?"]
[White "Puzzles"]
[Black "Le, Tuan Minh vs. Xiong, Jeffery"]
[FEN "1rb2rk1/6pp/pq2pp2/2ppP3/3P2n1/2PQP3/RP1NB1PP/4K2R b K - 0 17"]
[Result "*"]

17. c4 {Kicking white's queen away from defending the e3-pawn.} 
